<main>
    <h2>The Problem</h2>
    <p>
        Many students experience poor internet connection during online TLE classes. 
        Slow speeds and frequent disconnections make it difficult to complete activities and access online tools.
    </p>
    <p>
        This issue affects learning performance, participation, and overall classroom productivity.
    </p>
    <ul>
        <li>Interrupted online lessons</li>
        <li>Delayed submission of activities</li>
        <li>Difficulty accessing learning platforms</li>
        <li>Increased stress for students and teachers</li>
    </ul>
</main>

